==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Outshoot
<hw>Out*shoot"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To exceed or
excel in shooting; to shoot beyond.</def> <rj><au>Bacon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Men are resolved never to <qex>outshoot</qex> their forefathers'
mark.</q> <rj><qau>Norris.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Outshut</ent>⟦br⟧
